N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 150.3 - The navigation season

State Regulations

The opening of the navigation season depends upon natural
conditions. Notice of official opening and closing dates will be announced by
the Canal Corporation annually. Notes
